milestones.description: Clive Lloyd has become the top scorer for WI in ODIs with 434 runs, going past Viv Richards's 385
This is the highest match aggregate (456) involving teams West Indies & New Zealand in ODIs
Andy Roberts has become the top wicket-taker for WI in ODIs with 22 wickets, going past Holder's 19
Clive Lloyd has scored 4 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for WI breaking Viv Richards's record
Clive Lloyd has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (14) for WI, going past Deryck Murray
Clive Lloyd and Joel Garner's 40-run partnership is WI's highest for the 8th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 39 between Viv Richards and Holding
